<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Our Platform</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 6px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        margin: 20px auto;
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db, #2980b9);
        color: white;
        padding: 25px 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .header p {
        margin: 5px 0 0;
        opacity: 0.9;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px 25px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }
      .content h2 {
        color: #2980b9;
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 22px;
      }
      .content p {
        margin: 15px 0;
        color: #444;
      }
      .content ul {
        margin: 20px 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      .content ul li {
        margin: 10px 0;
        color: #444;
      }
      .feature-box {
        background-color: #f5f9fc;
        border-left: 3px solid #3498db;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .button-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 30px 0 20px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db, #2980b9);
        color: white;
        padding: 12px 30px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      }
      .button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #777777;
        border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      }
      .social-links {
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
      .social-links a {
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 0 5px;
      }
      @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
        .container {
          margin: 10px;
        }
        .header h1 {
          font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
          padding: 20px 15px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Our Platform!</h1>
        <p>We're delighted to have you join us</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
        
        <p>Thank you for creating your account with us. We're thrilled to welcome you to our community of professionals and look forward to helping you achieve your goals.</p>
        
        <p>Your account has been successfully created with: <strong>{{email}}</strong></p>
        
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h3>Getting Started</h3>
          <p>Here are some recommended first steps to make the most of your experience:</p>
          
          <ul>
            <li>Complete your profile to enhance your visibility</li>
            <li>Explore our comprehensive service offerings</li>
            <li>Connect with other professionals in your field</li>
            <li>Set up your notifications preferences</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="button-container">
          <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Access Your Account</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is ready to help you every step of the way. Simply reply to this email or contact our support center.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The {{companyName}} Team</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <div class="social-links">
          {{#if socialLinks}}
            {{#each socialLinks}}
              <a href="{{this.url}}" target="_blank">{{this.name}}</a>
            {{/each}}
          {{/if}}
        </div>
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>